cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY 

This paper presents a learning scheme using deep reinforcement learning and inverse dynamics model for robotic manipulation tasks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it involves learning algorithms. The paper also involves robotics and control, which suggests cs.RO (Robotics) as the second likely category. The use of deep learning and reinforcement learning also suggests cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) as possible categories. Finally, the paper involves control systems, which suggests cs.SY (Systems and Control) as a possible category.
